* Data Validation (Single Field): Shows runners with a specific missing field.
*   When to use:    Before race day or after participant import to check a specific field.
*   How to use:     Double-click, enter the field name to check (e.g., AGE, DIV, CHIP), and click OK.
Destination         Browse

Select              ?Enter field name to check (e.g., AGE, DIV, CHIP, SEX, RACE)
EQ

* The Field commands below are not used when Destination is Browse.
* Uncomment them if you change Destination to a text file (they define the output columns).
* Field               BIB
* Field               Name
* Field               Sex
* Field               AGE
* Field               DIV
* Field               CHIP
* Field               RACE
* Field               City
* Field               State